data.description: A 3 bedroom, 1 bath home sitting in the heart of Eveleth offering spacious living room, dining room, kitchen, and bedrooms. The kitchen has a lot of counter space and storage space. Main living area has a den/office space. 3 bedrooms upstairs. 1 stall detached garage.
